{"tid":1247042,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"係現場唔會咁得閒不停連登留言 請場波完結左先屌人 我地等緊大家夠鐘出黎","createTime":"2019-06-21T03:31:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-21T04:11:02.000Z","uid":79181,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"71301564f2101b9bb1f319ebcb832d4279e27d7b","tid":1247042,"uid":79181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T03:31:42.000Z","msg":"大家唔好灰心住<br />\n現場做好自己本份 唔好擔心太多 <br />\n同附近隊友交流下唔同情況要點做<br />\n有d人煙都未滅過或者冇經驗 <br />\n唔好離開人群太遠單拖幾件比人逗走<br />\n有好多人打算睇情況去支援<br />\n晏少少放工放學就會人多<br />\n <br />\n文宣冇出既人繼續做野同時注意現場情況<br />\n有咩物資現場唔夠就開post叫人帶黎<br />\n一味推d廢話post冇用<br />\n提醒未出既人合適衣物同物品<br />\n重新宣傳返法律知識同法律支援資訊<br />\n<br />\n最後場波成功/失敗/平手 先再屌人<br />\n唔該文宣幫個忙推有用既post同叫人<br />\n幫推"},{"pid":"e7797dd522a0d55340c6191c2136e60df019552d","tid":1247042,"uid":79181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T03:31:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cf87fda9a3e51137c59fe02ad18a719f5ddbad37","tid":1247042,"uid":79181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T03:33:11.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"1644b7d55d2ed1df0adf447f0ecb5d7b07dcd912","tid":1247042,"uid":79181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T03:33:50.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6c1ab8d5a4b0bd597b5f95264d2133fd4f2de0be","tid":1247042,"uid":79181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T03:34:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"71a353d6b15ebc284f8b56b30b6d455954e0dc45","tid":1247042,"uid":79181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T03:34:26.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c0140f8a03b0edb17290ad2afe43730dcf892b82","tid":1247042,"uid":79181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T03:34:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"792c3337e9e8cb70c1f156fcba91c7240e70beff","tid":1247042,"uid":79181,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-21T03:35:09.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"10caab26e867190a0333a2f76f516055f8504578","tid":1247042,"uid":79181,"like":0,"dislike"